# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Velosta — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.local.example .env.local

# ─── Required: Mapbox ───
# Sign up free at https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
# Copy your Default public token (starts with pk.)
# Free tier: 50,000 map loads/month — no credit card needed
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.your_mapbox_token_here

# ─── Optional: OpenAI (AI-Powered Itineraries) ───
# Get a key at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# If not set, the app uses the built-in local itinerary engine
# which generates quality itineraries from real POI data
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here

# ─── Future: Database ───
# PostgreSQL connection for real destination/experience data
# Not needed for current version (uses hardcoded data)
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/velosta
